Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:59.44,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰かのためなら　悪くはないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:05.28,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}理由らしいものは今日も見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:10.80,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}曖昧なリアル　点と点を繋ぐ光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:17.54,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}消えそうな夢をそっと握り締めてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:27.17,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}僕たちの声が　君の癒せない傷跡に届けば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:32.77,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}流れてく雲の速さへと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:38.79,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}置いてかれないように叫ぶ今日のエチュード
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:46.13,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えたい静かな絶望の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:51.04,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}新しい始まりへのページ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.78,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その手を取って　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:58.59,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}君が望むから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:02.05,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}どこまでもいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:59.44,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}若是為了誰  這無可厚非
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:05.28,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}今天依然沒看見像樣的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:10.80,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}曖昧交織的現實  點點相連的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:17.54,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嘗試著握住那轉眼即逝的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:27.17,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我們的聲音  若能傳達到你那無法治癒的傷痕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:32.77,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}宛如流雲的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:38.79,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}為了不再置之不理  放聲唱出今天的練習曲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:46.13,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}渴望著那寂靜的絕望的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:51.04,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是通向全新伊始的篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.78,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}牽住你的手  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:58.59,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}正如你所期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:02.05,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}一路向前


Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  浪費這麼多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好這是草壁家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35}玫歐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽好  保險箱裡有個包
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿上包快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.63,0:00:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別多問  照我的話去做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再打電話給我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天國的媽媽會守護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…

Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:15.98,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}翻譯:絆咲    Miya　校對:千葉命　後期:毛球／阿爽

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在深切感受到萬事開頭的重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬來這個城市的我 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛上學就遇到了篠崎彩夏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨之認識了聚集在拉麵店的NEET們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還被捲入了案件中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了不要加麵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用蔥來打掩護想矇混過關
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明老闆說想讓你稍微攝取點固態食物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了說了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才不小心把那瓶掉在地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和其他的比較一下就能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這一瓶還沒達到我喜歡的溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你還是多提升下觀察力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算哪門子的觀察力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.39,0:03:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好（泰語）

Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:13.86,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(500,0)}你與旅行包

Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  我臉上有什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你要做什麼  無禮之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  你簡直跟人偶沒有兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由自主地就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太失禮了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼女人小孩一看見我  就把我當寵物耍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你就是偵探嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是普通的偵探  是NEET偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEET偵探愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人說你這裡有難必救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這名片…你認識宏哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我叫玫歐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏哥之前住在隔壁姐姐家的時候給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生在泰國吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫歐是chww-len吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  你怎麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛進門的時候  你用泰語打招呼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chww-len是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chww-len就是一種暱稱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了驅邪不希望心愛之人被魔鬼抓走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就取一些動物或者無意義的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外玫歐在泰語中就是貓的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  別為了這種事來浪費我的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫歐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來聽聽吧  你的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好這是草壁家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35}玫歐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽好  保險箱裡有個包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿上包快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別多問  照我的話去做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再打電話給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天國的媽媽會守護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁昌也38歲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職業是行銷顧問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多次往返東南亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九年前與一位泰國女性結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛來日本是住在大阪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時令尊在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑道？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過很快就洗手不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說「為了玫歐和媽媽  會好好生活」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包裡的東西你看過了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不介意讓我看一下的話  就把包打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  一旦打開就無法回頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為一直以來害死人最多的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是炸藥也不是毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是情報  知即是死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己都不知道令尊正在經歷什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家有富裕到這個程度嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  完全不富裕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲這些錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？爸爸怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊可能牽涉進某起犯罪案當中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是他害怕東窗事發正在逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  爸爸不會這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是列舉可能性罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接了令尊電話後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾用公用電話給他手機打過一次電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒手機嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸說等我成年後就把媽媽用過的給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今後你這邊的聯絡需要特別謹慎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊也這樣說過吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一次  哪怕就給他報個平安…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  這是我接受你委託的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不委託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我  我要去找爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連他在哪都不知道  你怎麼找？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫歐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你眼前的是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是普通的偵探  是NEET偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要委託我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算搜遍大千世界 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會給你一個答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我對委託人應盡的禮儀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能找到爸爸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你相信我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  請救救爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人不才  但還請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  不過你可得好好照顧她啊鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過吃的只有拉麵而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  我是不是添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是歡迎你的最好證明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  一起整理房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你助手先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的人都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏哥也引以為豪地說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花丸是我的棲身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有個既溫柔又漂亮的「媽媽」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界唯一攻略不了的人原來是說明老闆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是個戀母的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來玫歐的媽媽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛來日本就因病去世了 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  玫歐還有爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸經常教導我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的家人不是由血緣相連的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:10:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活在同一屋簷下互相珍惜對方才是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫歐真是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像妹妹一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島同學有兄妹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹她負責給我做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親一年到頭都很少回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親也去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家父母已經分居了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也完全見不著哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上一次全家一起吃飯是什麼時候來著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要是能快點回來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海  給我揉揉肩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你女朋友幫你揉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  小白臉是服務行業一般都是幫她揉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好累好累
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是問遍了歷屆女友才得到這個的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真虧你能拿到手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這印子是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦  明知故問
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人總有一天會被捅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說是出錯了無法送出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你跑一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上黃網了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  什麼都沒看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯  才沒去過外國的色情網站
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  不愧是大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幫傢伙真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群傻瓜們給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  大哥很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名副其實的神之手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真的能成為即時戰力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不這樣  趁這機會乾脆和大哥結拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好！  那本幫就無敵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35}怎麼會演變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫裡不收學生  這是我們的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說這種傻話我就把他揍飛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從愛麗絲那聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去印五百張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命  我這就去磨練男子氣概
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們能做的僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲應該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  她說不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你一句忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:13:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想受傷就別再插手此事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前黑幫給了女兒兩億隨後消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼好兆頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是小鬼的偵探遊戲就能解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽懂了就趕快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經約定好要幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人能救多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頂多也就是身邊那些朋友們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不劃清界線  那可就沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此我還是想救她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒聽懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是想理解就能讓你挺身而出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是愛麗絲的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不對勁了就馬上跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒你的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又多了一個笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會說那種話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼你幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海幫大忙了  借我點錢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高中生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生日什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10月31日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天蠍座嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是黑道座
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是老頭子講笑話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然無視
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿哲  你這小弟很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼還有什麼想問的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁昌也  你認識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和他什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫老大跟他不是結拜兄弟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能透露些消息就是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼保證你不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的蛋蛋  這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽子倒是挺大的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁是專門給岸和田會洗帳的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗帳？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗黑錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是money  laundering
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在脫離幫會的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以接下這工作來取代切手指的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說草壁他私吞了岸和田會的黑錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  數額很大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有三億
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三億？不是兩億…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私吞三億夾帶私逃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還在大阪混的時候並不是像現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切為家人著想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想切手指就是因為這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口口聲聲說切了手指就沒法正常工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  肚子痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺今天一直都很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我也是第一次見尼莫老大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我把所有關西區黑道的話都套了個遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫老大算是中到大獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲哥  你為了僅有一面之緣的人都能拼上性命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫歐日本怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫歐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於打來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海現在馬上過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助手先生  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫歐  替換的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探的頭髮真的好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她卻一點都不愛護哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海  你在關鍵的時候真是派不上用場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我叫出來的理由就是這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題就在差的那一億了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是現在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道  不過根據這情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  玫歐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩夏  吹風機吹得我頭腦發熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能和玫歐到樓下幫忙給我拿冰淇淋上來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是兩頭不到岸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其拿走一億不如拿上三億和玫歐一起遠走高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是考慮確保利益吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其一次拿走三億
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如先分開藏到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分散風險是具有戰略意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是岸和田會的行動比預想快得多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已才把剩下的交給玫歐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他還打算回收玫歐和那兩億嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  估計不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方可是黑道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情敗露時就改變策略了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如把玫歐作為誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:18:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是他自己的女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他為什麼不讓玫歐帶電話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不接她電話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐的說法充其量只能算可能性之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先追查資金的動向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到草壁和岸和田會的接觸點才是首要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁先生應該會回來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現階段得不出任何結論
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得草壁先生不是那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果不重視玫歐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會說出「天國的媽媽會守護你的」這種話的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫歐  你有沒有從爸爸那裡聽到些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說回泰國之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼問？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不沒什麼  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助手先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸估計不會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定一個人逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說玫歐被拋棄了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸絕對不會做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會做這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸對玫歐說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫歐是最重要的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼永遠是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸跟玫歐約定好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種約定怎麼能當一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  就是約定好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我約定好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩夏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上玫歐的包  馬上過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海  你來看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理論得花上百年確立立足點方能到達的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信仰之翼卻能在一夜之間飛至
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天國的媽媽會守護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該更加單純地理解草壁這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  玫歐可能已經從直覺上得到答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親的清白  以及那句話的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就能喚來聖者之音…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.43,0:23:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫歐察覺到了的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.41,0:23:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁先生並沒有拋棄玫歐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到的事是…

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:12.02,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}路地裏には暗い暗い灯り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:16.50,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}そこに集う羽虫達のよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:20.71,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}もがく僕らは cry cry 共に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:25.19,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}秘めた想いをくすぶらせてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:29.86,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}何をすればいい？それが分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:34.21,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}無限の意味 恐れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:38.52,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}痺れを切らした両の足が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:44.74,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}立ち上がれとせがんでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:51.21,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}全て運命(さだめ)だなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:53.35,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}神の落書きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:55.83,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}丸めて捨てるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.01,0:22:59.89,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}たったひとつの冴えたやり方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.13,0:23:04.07,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}いつも胸に抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:10.13,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}夜明け睨みつけるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:12.02,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}小巷裡昏暗的燈光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:16.50,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}引得小飛蟲紛紛聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:20.71,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我們心急如焚一同哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:25.19,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}煽起深藏心中的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:29.86,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我不知該何去何從
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:34.21,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}無限的意義使我畏縮不前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:38.52,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}面對那失去知覺的雙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:44.74,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我央求道  快快站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:51.21,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}一切都是命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:53.35,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只是神輕描淡寫的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:55.83,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}看我把它揉成一團一併扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.01,0:22:59.89,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}唯一行之有效的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.13,0:23:04.07,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}就是謹記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:10.13,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}怒視拂曉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
